			<h1>Welcome to Deaf Children's Society!</h1>
			<h3><strong>are you...</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Seeking the best opportunities for your deaf or hard of hearing child?</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Looking for support, resources, and people who<br /></strong></em><em><strong>personally understand the needs of deaf and hard of hearing children?</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Gathering information and answers to your questions?</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>With more than 30 years of experience in supporting deaf children <br />and their families, DCS is the place for you.</strong></em></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">explore our website!</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">see all that DCS can offer you...</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, 'times new roman', serif; color: #773388; font-size: xx-large;"><span style="font-size: 27px; line-height: 34px; text-transform: lowercase;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, tahmoa, sans-serif; color: #111111; font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; text-transform: none;"><br /></span></span></strong></span></span></p>
		</div>
